Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,AGORA. Role-aware AI support agents for multi-app SSO ecosystems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Marines move across LMS, CMS, BBB, and Keycloak with different roles\Nin each. The AI assistant has to know who is asking before it answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixty doc chunks across four apps. Four demo personas, each with a\NJSON role and ABAC tree. Active persona: a Private at boot camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Joe asks how to pull a battalion-wide transcript report.\NPersona-aware RAG runs and the audit panel lists exactly what was …
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:01:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Same code path. Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and the assistant runs inside\Nthe SCIF. Identity, ABAC, and inference all on-prem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,AGORA. Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
